    "1 You a r e an a n t i n a 2D s i m u l a t i o n t a s k e d w i t h f i n d i n g f o o d, marking t h e p a t h t o f o o d w i t h pheromone t r a i l s, and u s i n g n e s t s c e n t t o n a v i g a t e b a c k t o t h e n e s t when c a r r y i n g f o o d.",
